<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %> - Portfolio</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar', { activePage: 'about' }) %>

    <!-- About Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <h1 class="hero-title">
                    About <span class="gradient-text">Me</span>
                </h1>
                <p class="hero-subtitle">
                    Backend Developer | API Architect | Microservices Engineer
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About Content -->
    <section class="about-detail">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="profile-section">
                <div class="profile-image">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1515378791036-0648a3ef77b2?w=400&h=400&fit=crop&crop=face" alt="Backend Developer">
                </div>
                <div class="profile-text">
                    <h2>Hi, I'm a Backend Developer ðŸ‘‹</h2>
                    <p>
                        I'm passionate about building scalable, efficient, and robust backend systems. Through the HNG Backend Internship, 
                        I've gained hands-on experience in building RESTful APIs, microservices, distributed systems, and integrating 
                        various technologies to solve real-world problems.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        My journey has taken me through multiple stages of backend development, from simple API endpoints to complex 
                        microservices architectures with message queues, payment integrations, and AI agent implementations.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        I believe in writing clean, maintainable code and following industry best practices. I'm always eager to learn 
                        new technologies and tackle challenging problems.
                    </p>
                    
                    <div class="contact-info">
                        <h3>Contact Information</h3>
                        <div class="contact-details">
                            <div class="contact-item">
                                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor">
