                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="skills-section">
                <h2>Technical Skills</h2>
                <div class="skills-grid">
                    <% skills.forEach(skill => { %>
                    <div class="skill-item"><%= skill %></div>
                    <% }) %>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="experience-section">
                <h2>Experience</h2>
                <div class="experience-card">
                    <h3><%= experience %></h3>
                    <ul class="experience-highlights">
                        <li>Built 8+ production-ready backend projects</li>
                        <li>Implemented RESTful APIs with proper authentication</li>
                        <li>Designed microservices architecture with message queues</li>
                        <li>Integrated external APIs (Paystack, REST Countries, Cat Facts)</li>
                        <li>Developed AI agents using Mastra framework</li>
                        <li>Worked with databases (PostgreSQL, MySQL, MongoDB, Redis)</li>
                        <li>Implemented CI/CD pipelines and Docker containerization</li>
                        <li>Collaborated in team projects using Git and Agile methodologies</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="journey-section">
                <h2>My Learning Journey</h2>
                <div class="timeline">
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="timeline-marker">0</div>
                        <div class="timeline-content">
                            <h3>Stage 0 - Profile API</h3>
                            <p>Started with basics: building a simple API endpoint with external API integration</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="timeline-marker">1</div>
                        <div class="timeline-content">
                            <h3>Stage 1 - String Analyzer</h3>
                            <p>Learned data processing, hashing, and complex filtering logic</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="timeline-marker">2</div>
                        <div class="timeline-content">
                            <h3>Stage 2 - Country Currency API</h3>
                            <p>Mastered database caching, multiple API integrations, and image generation</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="timeline-marker">3</div>
                        <div class="timeline-content">
                            <h3>Stage 3 - AI Agent</h3>
                            <p>Built intelligent agents with Mastra and integrated with Telex.im</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="timeline-marker">4</div>
                        <div class="timeline-content">
                            <h3>Stage 4 - Notification System</h3>
                            <p>Architected microservices with RabbitMQ, circuit breakers, and service discovery</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="timeline-marker">7</div>
                        <div class="timeline-content">
                            <h3>Stage 7 - Auth & API Keys</h3>
                            <p>Implemented JWT authentication and API key management systems</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="timeline-marker">8</div>
                        <div class="timeline-content">
                            <h3>Stage 8 - Wallet Service</h3>
                            <p>Integrated Paystack payments, webhooks, and built a complete wallet system</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2025 Backend Developer Portfolio. Built with Node.js, TypeScript & EJS</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>

<style>
.about-detail {
    padding: 4rem 0;
}

.profile-section {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 4rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.profile-image {
    flex: 0 0 250px;
}

.profile-image img {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 250px;
    height: 250px;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    border: 3px solid var(--primary);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px var(--shadow);
}

.profile-text {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 300px;
}

.profile-text h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
}

.profile-text p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.contact-info {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
}

.contact-info h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
}

.contact-details {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
}

.contact-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
}

.contact-item svg {
    color: var(--primary);
    flex-shrink: 0;
}

.skills-section,
.experience-section,
.journey-section {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
}

.skills-section h2,
.experience-section h2,
.journey-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
}

.skills-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(150px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
}

.skill-item {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    text-align: center;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--primary);
    transition: all 0.3s;
}

.skill-item:hover {
    border-color: var(--primary);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.2);
}

.experience-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
}

.experience-card h3 {
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
}

.experience-highlights {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
}

.experience-highlights li {
    padding: 0.75rem 0;
    padding-left: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
}

.experience-highlights li::before {
    content: 'â–¹';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--primary);
    font-weight: bold;
}

.timeline {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 2rem;
}

.timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
}

.timeline-item {
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
}

.timeline-marker {
    position: absolute;
    left: -2.75rem;
    width: 3rem;
    height: 3rem;
    background: var(--bg-dark);
    border: 3px solid var(--primary);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--primary);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
}

.timeline-content {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    margin-left: 2rem;
    transition: all 0.3s;
}

.timeline-content:hover {
    border-color: var(--primary);
    transform: translateX(5px);
}

.timeline-content h3 {
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

.timeline-content p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .profile-section {
        flex-direction: column;
        text-align: center;
        gap: 2rem;
    }
    
    .profile-image {
        flex: 0 0 auto;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }
    
    .profile-text {
        text-align: left;
    }
    
    .skills-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(120px, 1fr));
    }
    
    .timeline {
        padding-left: 1rem;
    }
    
    .timeline-marker {
        left: -2rem;
        width: 2.5rem;
        height: 2.5rem;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    
    .timeline-content {
        margin-left: 1.5rem;
    }
}

@media (max-width: 480px) {
    .profile-image img {
        max-width: 200px;
        height: 200px;
    }
    
    .skills-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
}
</style>